<author>shyl mdạnạt, lḥn ạ̉jnby</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lwlạ ạlṣlyb mn ạ̉nạ yạ sydy lwlạk yạ fạdy ḥyạty mn ạ̉:wn
 lwlạk knt tạỷhaⁿạ fy ẓlmty wkạn qlby gẖạrqaⁿạ tḥt ạldywn
 ạlqrạr- fạ̉nạ lk wlgẖyrk ln ạ̉kwn wlạ̉jlk kl tḍḥyẗ thwn
 lys mtẖlk mn yḥbny bfw̉ạdh ạlḥnwn
 2- lwlạ ạntẓạry lmjyỷk ạlqryb lwlạ rjạỷy fy ḥyạty fy ạlsmạʾ
 lʿsẖt ṭwl ạlʿmr fy kẖwf mdẖyb mn ạlgẖd ạlmjhwl fy lyl ạlsẖqạʾ
 3- ạ̉kwn fy ạldnyạ srạbaⁿạ ynthy ạ̹n knt qd ḥrmt mn ạ̉mjạdk
 mwlạy ạ̉sẖkr ạmtyạzk ạldẖy qd ḍmny wạkẖtrạny lbytk</lyrics>
<title>lwlạ ạlṣlyb</title>
</song>